Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.57,0:00:10.65,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.98,0:00:19.17,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.34,0:00:36.30,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Black Market.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.30,0:00:42.31,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit dangerous, but they have \Nsome very effective magical items.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.31,0:00:45.31,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, I lost again! Bah-ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.43,0:00:50.32,main,Old lady,0000,0000,0000,,I can see the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:52.82,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,That old lady's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.39,0:00:56.41,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I really shouldn't be \Nwasting time here, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.89,0:00:59.53,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, she's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.88,0:01:00.70,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.70,0:01:05.75,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Market is no place \Nfor you lovely ladies. Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.75,0:01:07.54,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost, you insect.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.87,0:01:08.71,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.71,0:01:12.59,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I found something really cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.59,0:01:14.39,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.39,0:01:16.22,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.77,0:01:19.21,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hey, you're Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.21,0:01:20.64,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,It's Sekke! Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.11,0:01:22.78,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How've you been, Bah-ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.78,0:01:26.14,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,The name's Bah-ha! No, wait, Sekke!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:27.35,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.02,0:01:30.09,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I took the Entrance Exam with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.57,0:01:32.86,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you're a member of the \NGreen Praying Mantises.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.86,0:01:37.88,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,He's with two beautiful girls?! Wait, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.88,0:01:40.87,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,They're both members of \Nthe Black Bulls, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:45.22,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, you bastard! \NYou're making me jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.67,0:01:52.09,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's all your fault that \NI ended up in the Green Praying Mantises.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:55.92,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha! You infuriating bah-hastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:21.41,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,750)}The Wizard King Saw
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:25.74,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Grey words can't make anything happen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.74,0:02:28.41,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, yeah I know
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:33.66,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wishing to fly freely across the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.66,0:02:36.00,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I dreamed it all my life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.00,0:02:39.55,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Step by step I go, though \Nit's a doubtful world 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:41.55,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't care how much I fall
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:45.02,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Instinct is my guide, I never give up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:51.31,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To faraway future, I burst out running
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:56.78,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Go beyond even the unseen fears
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:03:01.86,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The vision I had, so I can be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:07.12,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday I will write the next page
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:10.62,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You are my hope
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:13.38,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Like that page from someday
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:15.71,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to meet you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:18.67,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I call this a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:28.77,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Are you out shopping with these girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:30.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Well, today's our day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.53,0:03:32.56,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha! Must be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.03,0:03:36.65,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's your day off, shouldn't \Nyou be finding some basic tasks
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:39.21,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,to do for points,\Ninstead of messing around?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:41.95,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the Black Bulls \Nhave negative stars—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:44.51,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Stars! Oh, yeah! Listen to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.51,0:03:48.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We got a star from the\N Wizard King on our first mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:51.62,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:55.14,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:58.26,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,They're serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:00.76,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:03.78,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha, bah-ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:07.01,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see! Seems like you're working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:08.22,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Bah-ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:09.63,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,It's Sekke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:11.41,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I... The other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.41,0:04:14.09,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I-I got my second star...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.23,0:04:24.99,main,Old lady,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:29.74,main,Old lady,0000,0000,0000,,My winnings! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:36.08,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,That old lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:45.58,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,He's got some nerve,\N stealing in front of Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:49.43,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding. But everything will be \Nfine if we leave it to the little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:51.24,main,Old lady,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.24,0:04:52.22,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:55.67,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to let you \Nsteal all the glory, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.67,0:05:00.17,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bronze Creation Magic: Sekke Shooting Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:01.89,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.89,0:05:03.02,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:08.87,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this to me. You lovely ladies \Ncan go relax with that old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:11.06,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Ew!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:12.02,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:14.54,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:17.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.93,0:05:22.06,main,Theif,0000,0000,0000,,Just try and catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.06,0:05:24.09,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, dang it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:36.09,main,Old guy,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.61,0:05:40.69,main,ASta,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:44.13,main,Theif,0000,0000,0000,,I finally lost him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.66,0:05:46.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:47.81,main,Theif,0000,0000,0000,,He's so damn persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:53.91,main,Theif,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.97,0:06:02.71,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not letting you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:06.30,main,Thief,0000,0000,0000,,How is he catching up to me \Nwhen he's only running?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:09.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do something about that cloud,\Nor I'll never catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.42,0:06:12.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a cloud created by magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:13.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:20.70,main,Thief,0000,0000,0000,,Do you actually think you can cut \Nthrough my Bandit's Cloud Wind—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:23.94,main,Thief,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:28.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.59,0:06:34.99,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:36.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:38.79,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take the glory on this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:41.52,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.52,0:06:43.09,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.83,0:06:49.10,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha! You're under arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.10,0:06:52.59,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,He's my prey! Bah-hahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:55.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-hahaha... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:06:57.98,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:01.25,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:03.40,main,Thief,0000,0000,0000,,Knock off that stupid laugh of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:06.82,main,Thief,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking you down with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.31,0:07:14.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Bah-ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.39,0:07:23.04,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Poison... Poison's coursing through me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:25.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:27.75,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah... ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.35,0:07:31.76,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Am I going to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:37.01,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, I was \Nonce trying to get to the top, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:38.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:43.44,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I hate that I have to leave \Neverything to him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:47.94,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,You're the man who defeated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:51.70,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Make it all the way to the \Ntop for my sake, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:55.61,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving my dream to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:56.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.71,0:07:59.04,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-haha...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:06.11,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I guess going out like this isn't so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.58,0:08:08.55,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah... ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.53,0:08:14.22,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha! Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:19.94,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I'm not dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:22.66,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:26.10,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:29.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave something so important with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.18,0:08:33.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Survive and make your own dream come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:36.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:41.16,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. There's no way this would kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.55,0:08:42.71,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:45.29,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a momentary numbing poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:48.74,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Put this Shique ointment on it,\Nand you'll be better in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.65,0:08:59.83,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha! Make sure you stay diligent \Nuntil the next time I see you, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:02.27,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:04.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:08.69,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,On the outside, our little boy \Ndefinitely looks younger than him,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:11.79,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems our little boy is \Nmuch stronger on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:16.67,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let it get taken again, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:21.79,main,Old lady,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.21,0:09:24.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:25.57,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:27.06,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Live a long, happy life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:34.55,main,Old lady,0000,0000,0000,,Magic negation, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:38.39,main,Old lady,0000,0000,0000,,That's a type of magic \NI've never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.55,0:09:44.81,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Actually... is that even magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.26,0:09:49.81,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Yami sure took in an interesting kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:53.90,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I can't stop \Nwandering around in disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.41,0:09:56.89,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,I finally found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:09:58.12,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.12,0:10:00.57,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world are you doing, Wizard King?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:06.60,sign_14400_150_28th_Wizard_King,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1031,995)}28th Wizard King\N{\fs30}Julius Novachrono
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:07.87,top,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing? I'm strolling through \Nthe castle town looking for new magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:11.67,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Have you any \Nawareness of your position?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.45,0:10:15.09,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Encounters with magic are once in a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:16.33,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:19.61,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,You never know what kind of magic \Nyou're going to encounter and where.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:22.39,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, you magic nerd!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:25.77,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, calm down, Marx.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:31.27,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the new kid from William's squad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:40.10,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm off to encounter even \Nmore new magic. I'll be back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:43.49,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:59.51,sign_14400_150_28th_Wizard_King,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Member of the Golden Dawn\N{\fs30}Klaus Lunettes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:11:00.39,italicstop,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,The Golden Dawn's new recruit, Yuno...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:04.55,sign_14400_150_28th_Wizard_King,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1013)}Member of the Golden Dawn\N{\fs30}Yuno
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.06,0:11:05.85,italicstop,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,The candidate that every Magic Knight \NCaptain wanted at the Entrance Exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:11.69,sign_14400_150_28th_Wizard_King,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Member of the Golden Dawn\N{\fs30}Mimosa Vermillion
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.17,0:11:10.98,italicstop,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,And then we have the other new recruit,\N Mimosa Vermillion, from the royal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:13.85,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Their first mission is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:18.43,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,to act as bodyguards \Nfor Salim de Hapshass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.55,0:11:24.12,flashback,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We are to escort the son of Hapshass,\Nwho serves in the House of Lords,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:26.65,flashback,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,to our ally, the Heart Kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:30.04,flashback,William,0000,0000,0000,,You know who Lord Hapshass is, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:31.58,flashback,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I know his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.89,0:11:37.55,flashback,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I've only heard negative things about him,\Nsuch as that he's new money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.25,0:11:43.00,flashback,William,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that's why he's worried that his son, \Nwho is going to study in the Heart Kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:46.06,flashback,William,0000,0000,0000,,might be attacked by bandits on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:51.73,flashback,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,But there are many powerful mages \Namong the lord's family...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.82,0:11:58.22,flashback,William,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, he feels having Magic Knights\Nact as his bodyguards will be safer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:12:03.83,flashback,William,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Hapshass makes very generous \Ndonations to the Magic Knights every year,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:06.88,flashback,William,0000,0000,0000,,so it's rather hard to decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.88,0:12:08.09,flashback,William,0000,0000,0000,,Do you object?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.09,0:12:09.41,flashback,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.47,0:12:15.63,flashback,William,0000,0000,0000,,We need to accept every kind of mission. \NThat will also benefit the Clover Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.95,0:12:17.95,flashback,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. I am aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.95,0:12:20.38,flashback,William,0000,0000,0000,,Take Mimosa with you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:24.05,flashback,William,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure with you along as their mentor,\N they'll be more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:28.26,flashback,William,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you to \Nlook after the new recruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:35.73,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Salim de Hapshass lost to Yuno in the final \Npart of the Magic Knights Entrance Exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:39.61,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,He ended up being unable \Nto join the Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.18,0:12:43.95,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,So why was Yuno appointed \Nas one of his bodyguards?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:46.95,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,My first mission... I'm so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:51.16,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus, Yuno, it's a \Npleasure to work with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.86,0:12:53.00,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.42,0:12:55.13,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your guard down, Mimosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.13,0:12:56.65,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.65,0:12:57.63,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,That goes for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.01,0:12:59.46,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:01.53,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You insolent newbie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:09.47,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,How have you been, Yuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.05,0:13:14.05,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look so scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:18.98,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,I requested you as my bodyguard \Nbecause I want to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:21.86,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that you intend to \Nbecome the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.05,0:13:24.86,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:29.39,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,You were chosen by all of the captains. \NYou could've joined any squad,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:34.37,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,and you ended up choosing the \NGolden Dawn, so I had a feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.05,0:13:37.13,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,The more you achieve from now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.13,0:13:41.22,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,the more your name will spread \Nthroughout the kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:45.15,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno, the one who bears the \Nfour-leaf clover grimoire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:50.31,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure your dream of becoming \Nthe Wizard King comes true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:54.91,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,And then I'll be able to \Nbrag to my future children
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:58.14,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,that I once fought the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:14:02.40,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,And then they'll say, "Daddy, you're so cool!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:06.06,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,We have some time before we \Nget to the Heart Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.06,0:14:08.89,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,Could you tell me a little \Nmore about yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.59,0:14:11.41,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,I won't pester you if you're not up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:14.08,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm from Hage Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.81,0:14:21.75,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard of it. It's a village \Nin the Forsaken Realm, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:25.81,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's where the legend \Nof the first Wizard King
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.81,0:14:28.10,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,who defeated the demons comes from.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:33.11,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just a legend. A giant \Ndemon skull is actually still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:34.01,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.38,0:14:39.44,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, I was found abandoned in \Nfront of a church when I was a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:44.44,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen my parents,\Nand I have no idea who they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:50.70,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,The church was very poor, but the father \Nand sister there took very good care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:52.29,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very grateful to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.25,0:14:52.77,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,No problems so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.77,0:14:55.42,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,but there must be someone \Nin the Hapshass family
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.42,0:14:57.11,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,who can use transportation magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:14:58.71,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,How did we get stuck with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.43,0:15:01.71,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, we're the only bodyguards.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:07.42,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,If there was a real threat of an attack, \Nwouldn't they have more bodyguards?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.14,0:15:10.82,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,There are too many unknowns on this mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:12.82,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:14.89,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:21.39,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Those clouds...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:23.73,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,They're a little creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.99,0:15:26.52,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go check them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:30.18,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! No one said you could—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:32.74,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Be on your guard, Mimosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:34.23,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:51.76,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno, protect the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.12,0:15:54.01,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I intend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.09,0:16:02.77,main,Muha,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:48.52,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,That was magnificent!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.18,0:16:53.53,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Were those men not after Salim?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:03.79,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me back there. Well done, Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:07.50,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even have the opportunity \Nto use my Lightning God Rising Salim.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.23,0:17:10.43,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,I'm even more interested in you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:15.50,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,I know. Why don't you take me to your town?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:19.13,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see the place where you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:23.86,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know where you had \Nto live to grow up so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.86,0:17:26.73,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Salim, that's rather out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:29.33,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, given what just happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:31.61,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,we don't know what else \Nmight happen along the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:33.96,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,so we should head straight \Nfor the Heart Kingdom—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.96,0:17:39.01,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who may come after me,\N you three will protect me, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:41.13,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.13,0:17:44.12,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,But for nobility to go to a peasant \Nvillage in the Forsaken Realm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:46.70,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,It'll just be a quick stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.70,0:17:47.91,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.91,0:17:52.80,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Yuno would like to see \Neveryone back at his church, too. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:54.89,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,That's not your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:56.22,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.19,0:18:03.56,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the demon's skull!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:13.81,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite big. And on top of it is \Na statue of the first Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.58,0:18:18.45,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So where is this church?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:19.90,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:28.46,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.81,0:18:30.29,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:32.45,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:34.30,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:36.39,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,You've grown so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.81,0:18:41.82,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't changed. It's only \Nbeen two months since I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:46.31,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Really? But... Yes. Your face has matured.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:48.64,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,You look more like an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:50.48,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:53.31,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,We're stopping by briefly during our mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.01,0:18:56.93,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Why must I visit this village \Nin the Forsaken Realm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.93,0:19:00.57,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um, hello. I'm Sister Lily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.59,0:19:08.33,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Klaus Lunettes of the honorable \NGolden Dawn, led by William Vangeance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:10.08,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a mentor to these new recruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.45,0:19:14.17,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Klaus. Thank you \Nfor looking after Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:17.09,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard of you from Yuno's letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:18.49,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Letters?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:20.84,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What did you write about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:24.10,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.95,0:19:28.18,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mimosa Vermillion,\N one of Yuno's colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:30.69,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard of you, too, Mimosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:31.56,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:34.33,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,What did you write about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.32,0:19:37.82,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, what a beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:39.50,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:44.14,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,I am from Hapshass Village,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:49.58,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,the son of Lord Hapshass and the heir to \Nthe Hapshass family, Salim de Hapshass.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.30,0:19:52.33,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pleasure to make your acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.66,0:19:57.54,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I-I'm so sorry! I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.54,0:20:00.74,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it's all right, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.70,0:20:08.10,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno! It's Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:10.41,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,How are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.41,0:20:12.48,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:14.37,main,Recca,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here, Yuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.37,0:20:17.43,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, that robe's awesome! \NThat's the Golden Dawn's.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.43,0:20:18.78,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,It's the real thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:20.90,main,Arlu,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, it's Yuno! Yay! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:22.16,main,Arlu,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.16,0:20:23.77,main,Arlu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.77,0:20:24.99,main,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.44,0:20:27.71,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Are you keeping in contact with Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.71,0:20:28.88,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:31.95,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Are you staying the night tonight?\N You are, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.95,0:20:33.00,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.38,0:20:36.10,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, we're just stopping by.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.51,0:20:38.71,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We have to hurry on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:40.34,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Aww!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:44.06,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, we don't have \Nto be in such a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.06,0:20:46.46,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,We can spare an hour or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.46,0:20:47.43,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.53,0:20:52.89,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll prepare \Nsome famous Hage tato dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:54.44,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno, stay and have some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.95,0:20:57.32,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,That goes for all of you. Please, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.32,0:20:59.98,main,Salim,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, what a splendid church.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:04.89,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen such a \Ntiny church. It's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.89,0:21:06.11,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Tiny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.11,0:21:07.91,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a playhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:09.35,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.13,0:21:12.91,main,Recca,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno, tell us about the Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:14.37,main,Arlu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.37,0:21:15.62,main,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,Us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.23,0:21:19.29,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Why must I enter such a filthy little church?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:41.54,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can escape from here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.99,0:21:48.29,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Once again in the small closed off classroom
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.01,0:21:56.58,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The star of the class was shining yet again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.13,0:22:02.98,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,They shine so bright that I close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.97,0:22:06.47,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought many times
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:10.18,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,That the revolution was within my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.18,0:22:17.72,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it strange? If you want \Nto laugh, go ahead and laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.72,0:22:24.61,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of us who were left \Nbehind wanted to become something
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.61,0:22:31.87,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We repeat the same morning over and over
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.87,0:22:38.75,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who \Ncan choose your tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:43.42,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go beyond our current selves
